{"_path":"/maps/_ai/data-processing","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"数据处理 (Data Processing)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"数据处理-data-processing"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据处理 (Data Processing)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"nemo-curatorgpu-加速的企业级数据整理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NeMo Curator：GPU 加速的企业级数据整理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NeMo Curator 是 NVIDIA 推出的企业级数据整理工具包，专为大规模生成式 AI 训练设计。它利用 RAPIDS 库（cuDF、cuML、cuGraph）实现 GPU 加速，配合 Ray 支持多节点分布式扩展。在 DGX 系统上可在数小时内处理 TB 级语料，比传统 CPU 方案快 10-100 倍。支持文档提取、文本清洗、精确/模糊去重、质量评分和 PII 检测等模块化管道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/NVIDIA-NeMo/Curator","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NeMo Curator GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.nvidia.com/nemo/curator/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NVIDIA 官方文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developer.nvidia.cn/blog/streamlining-data-processing-for-domain-adaptive-pretraining-with-nvidia-nemo-curator/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ChipNeMo 案例"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"ray-data分布式数据加载与预处理"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ray Data：分布式数据加载与预处理"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ray Data 是 Ray 生态系统中的数据层，提供可扩展的数据加载、转换和传输能力。它与 PyTorch、TensorFlow、HuggingFace 无缝集成，支持从单机扩展到千节点集群。关键特性包括流式处理（无需全部载入内存）、自动分片（与分布式训练对齐）、以及 CPU 预处理 + GPU 训练的流水线并行。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.ray.io/en/latest/data/data.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ray Data 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.anyscale.com/blog/fast-flexible-scalable-data-loading-for-ml-training-with-ray-data","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ray Data 博客"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"minhash-lsh大规模近似去重"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MinHash + LSH：大规模近似去重"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MinHash 结合局部敏感哈希（LSH）是大规模数据集去重的标准算法。通过计算文档的签名并比较相似度，可以高效识别重复或高度相似的文档。研究表明这是 LLM 预训练数据去重的最合适算法，Data-Juicer 的实现在 8 节点 1280 CPU 核心上可在 3 小时内完成 TB 级数据集去重。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1007/978-3-031-82481-4_27","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MinHash LSH 去重研究"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zilliz.com/blog/data-deduplication-at-trillion-scale-solve-the-biggest-bottleneck-of-llm-training","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zilliz 万亿级去重"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"数据质量分层tier-1-3-体系"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据质量分层：Tier 1-3 体系"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"高质量数据应分为多个层级训练：Tier 1 是人工精选（Wikipedia、书籍、学术论文），Tier 2 是自动过滤后的 Web 数据（Common Crawl 子集），Tier 3 是代码、对话等专项数据。训练时按不同比例混合各层级数据，可显著提升模型泛化能力并减少数据污染。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2107.06499","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Deduplicating Training Data 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2101.00027","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Pile 数据集论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"数据混合策略决定模型能力的关键"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"数据混合策略：决定模型能力的关键"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不同来源数据的比例对模型能力有显著影响：代码数据比例提升会增强推理能力，对话数据比例提升会增强指令遵循能力，Web 数据比例提升会扩展知识广度但引入噪声。精心设计的数据混合策略是训练高性能模型的核心 secret sauce。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://huggingface.co/spaces/HuggingFaceFW/blogpost-fineweb-v1","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"FineWeb 技术报告"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://datacomp.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DataComp 基准"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"nemo-curatorgpu-加速的企业级数据整理","depth":2,"text":"NeMo Curator：GPU 加速的企业级数据整理"},{"id":"ray-data分布式数据加载与预处理","depth":2,"text":"Ray Data：分布式数据加载与预处理"},{"id":"minhash-lsh大规模近似去重","depth":2,"text":"MinHash + LSH：大规模近似去重"},{"id":"数据质量分层tier-1-3-体系","depth":2,"text":"数据质量分层：Tier 1-3 体系"},{"id":"数据混合策略决定模型能力的关键","depth":2,"text":"数据混合策略：决定模型能力的关键"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:data-processing.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/data-processing.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/data-processing","_extension":"md"}